OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777449958
OL,3,CBelgium sees rise in small boat
OL,4,Ccrossing attempts as routes shift from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FITV News Reporter Sam Holder speaks to
OL,8,FBelgian police about a shift in the
OL,9,Fway people smugglers on the continent
OL,10,Fare operating
OL,12,FPolice in Belgium say small boat
OL,13,Fcrossing attempts to the UK have risen
OL,14,Fsharply in recent months, with
OL,15,Factivity spreading along much of the
OL,16,Fcountry's coastline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
