CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777449958
OL,3,CBelgium sees rise in small boat
OL,4,Ccrossing attempts as routes shift from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FLast year, there were just two
OL,8,Fattempted small boat crossings
OL,9,Fcarrying migrants to Britain. But
OL,10,Fbetween January and April this year,
OL,11,Fthere have already been 32.
OL,13,FOnly five have been stopped before
OL,14,Fthey made it to the water.
OL,16,FIn the summer, when the weather is
OL,17,Fmore favourable for crossing the
OL,18,FChannel, the number of attempts is
OL,19,Fexpected to rise significantly.
OL,21,FBut why is this happening?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777449958
OL,3,CBelgium sees rise in small boat
OL,4,Ccrossing attempts as routes shift from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FThe people smugglers have started
OL,8,Fcoming over the border from France,
OL,9,Fwhere the majority of crossings still
OL,10,Ftake place, in response to the French
OL,11,Fpolice in Calais and Dunkirk taking a
OL,12,Ftougher stance in recent months.
OL,14,F"Since the beginning of this year,
OL,15,Fthere's a lot more police presence in
OL,16,FFrance and there's a lot more checks,"
OL,17,FAn Berger, from Belgium's Federal
OL,18,FPolice, told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777449958
OL,3,CBelgium sees rise in small boat
OL,4,Ccrossing attempts as routes shift from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,F"The smuggling organisations try to
OL,8,Ffind other ways ` the path of least
OL,9,Fresistance."
OL,11,FThe smugglers transport the migrants
OL,12,Ffrom places like Dunkirk to places
OL,13,Falong the Belgian coast in cars and
OL,14,Fvans ` occasionally they tell the
OL,15,Fmigrants to book an Uber ` where they
OL,16,Fhide until a second vehicle delivers a
OL,17,Fpackaged boat, which then needs to be
OL,18,Finflated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777449958
OL,3,CBelgium sees rise in small boat
OL,4,Ccrossing attempts as routes shift from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FUntil recently, the smugglers and
OL,8,Fmigrants had been using abandoned
OL,9,FWorld War Two bunkers as hiding
OL,10,Fplaces, which provided shelter from
OL,11,Fboth the elements and the infrared
OL,12,Fcameras used by police helicopters and
OL,13,Fdrones.
OL,15,FIn response, the Belgian authorities
OL,16,Fhave now sealed all the previously
OL,17,Fopen bunkers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777449958
OL,3,CBelgium sees rise in small boat
OL,4,Ccrossing attempts as routes shift from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FOnce inflated, the boats are often
OL,8,Fcarried by the migrants through the
OL,9,Fmiddle of coastal towns, on roads with
OL,10,Fblocks of flats on either side, like
OL,11,Fin Koksijde.
OL,13,F"There was somebody living in an
OL,14,Fapartment who was woken up because
OL,15,Fthey were carrying the boat and they
OL,16,Fhit a traffic sign, which made a lot
OL,17,Fof noise," Christian De Ridder, deputy
OL,18,Fchief of the West Coast Police Force,
OL,19,Ftold ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777449958
OL,3,CBelgium sees rise in small boat
OL,4,Ccrossing attempts as routes shift from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,F"He looked down and saw these guys
OL,8,Fcarrying the boat over to the sea."
OL,10,FDe Ridder says the crossings are "a
OL,11,Fvery important issue" for Belgium, not
OL,12,Fjust out of concern for preventing
OL,13,Fpeople smuggling but also for the
OL,14,Fimpact it could have on tourism.
OL,16,FThe police in Belgium use helicopters
OL,17,Fto scan the beaches and have teams
OL,18,Fthat try to intercept boats before
OL,19,Fthey reach the water, but they say
OL,20,Fthat is the last line of defence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777449958
OL,3,CBelgium sees rise in small boat
OL,4,Ccrossing attempts as routes shift from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FMuch of the focus is on preventing the
OL,8,Fsmugglers from getting into Belgium
OL,9,Ffrom France, with "intelligence-led"
OL,10,Fchecks on vehicles suspected of
OL,11,Fcarrying migrants on cross-border
OL,12,Froads and searches for any equipment
OL,13,Fwhich could be used to build or
OL,14,Finflate a small boat.
OL,16,FStill, there have been 27 occasions in
OL,17,Ffour months that smugglers have
OL,18,Fsuccessfully reached the shoreline
OL,19,Fwithout being stopped.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777449958
OL,3,CBelgium sees rise in small boat
OL,4,Ccrossing attempts as routes shift from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FOnce in the water, the Belgian naval
OL,13,Fpolice refuse to attempt to intercept
OL,14,Fthe boats because they say they are
OL,15,Fconcerned it could lead to migrants on
OL,16,Fboard drowning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777449958
OL,3,CBelgium sees rise in small boat
OL,4,Ccrossing attempts as routes shift from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FThe route the smugglers and migrants
OL,8,Ftake is to follow the Belgian coast to
OL,9,FFrance and then to cross the Channel
OL,10,Fat a similar point to if they had
OL,11,Fdeparted from Dunkirk.
OL,13,FA recent attempt from Knokke, near the
OL,14,Fborder with the Netherlands, meant the
OL,15,Fmigrants had to travel an additional
OL,16,F45 miles at sea before they even
OL,17,Fattempted to cross the Channel ` even
OL,18,Fmore danger on an already perilous
OL,19,Fjourney.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777449958
OL,3,CBelgium sees rise in small boat
OL,4,Ccrossing attempts as routes shift from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FThe Belgian authorities insist that
OL,8,Fstopping the departures is a priority
OL,9,Fand that they do not want their
OL,10,Fcoastal towns to end up like Calais
OL,11,Fand Dunkirk.
OL,13,FThe reality is that they don't appear
OL,14,Fto have enough police officers to
OL,15,Fadequately prevent crossings over such
OL,16,Fa long stretch of coast.
OL,18,FTheir hope is that their "intelligence-
OL,19,Fled" operations on the border will
OL,20,Fmake up the shortfall.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
